Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Sanctions against Libya
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xphk
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Jan 1986
Gaddafi's public support of airport terrorists prompts US into imposing sanctions against Libya. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less